item.description:
arXiv:2412.02281v1 Announce Type: new 
Abstract: We prove a connection formula for the basic hypergeomtric function ${}_n\varphi_{n-1}\left(
  a_1,...,a_{n-1},0;
  b_1,...,b_{n-1}
  ; q, z\right)$ by using the $q$-Borel resummation. As an application, we compute $q$-Stokes matrices of a special confluent hypergeometric $q$-difference system with an irregular singularity. We show that by letting $q\rightarrow 1$, the $q$-Stokes matrices recover the known expressions of the Stokes matrices of the corresponding confluent hypergeometric differential system.
